{"tid":2031110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我讀法律想講下點解有國安法冇23條出現","createTime":"2020-05-23T07:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T08:29:22.000Z","uid":36788,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e72bdd9204fff4503ccb426c3d636addb4740980","tid":2031110,"uid":36788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T07:39:46.000Z","msg":"借朋友AC<br />\n<br />\n當然我係光復香港時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係好多冇讀法律既人，唔明點解突然炸個國安法落黎。<br />\n<br />\n我以下說話會用人話講野，唔會用法律術語講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身香港傾左好耐立23條呢個惡法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但香港人知道有23就冇言論自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然一直反佢一直屌7鼠王芬呢班支持23條立法既傻鳩<br />\n所以23一直立唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年6月反送中開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟據基本法<br />\n中央係可以唔透過立會立法好似而家咁直接立法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係法例寫到明可以夾硬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以見班廢物23都立唔到所以自己黎料<br />\n因為係共產黨眼中<br />\n冇野比一個中國既原則更重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以國安法誕生，屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0aea5913908959f14346e776c4fac03a21ee85","tid":2031110,"uid":36788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T07:41:26.000Z","msg":"共產黨做野最出名夾硬黎，佢要贏可以再仆街既招都做得出，係基因問題"},{"pid":"73b0c761d7347bf314f44a2366625a634c87f941","tid":2031110,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T07:42:39.000Z","msg":"擁護基本法<br />\n然後基本法一早講左自己係零"},{"pid":"51746bed80c7c3e5ef2f7f82f2b0de783290b00b","tid":2031110,"uid":36788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73b0c761d7347bf314f44a2366625a634c87f941","tid":2031110,"uid":264245,"li